import React from 'react'
import Navbar from './Navbar'
import Home from './Home'
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'
import { CssBaseline } from '@mui/material'

const Layout=()=> {
  return <>
   <CssBaseline/>
    <Navbar/>
    <Home />
    <Outlet />
    </>;
}

export default Layout;
